data.description: Discover larger family home in the heart of Buckeye, AZ. This 2,676 square foot, 4 bedroom/3 bathroom home with a large loft/playroom upstairs is available to your family. Enjoy vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, SS appliances, breakfast bar with large kitchen and great room concept. View this home today and see the potential for your family! This home is in the heart of Buckeye, AZ. Within walking distance to parks and elementary school. You will not be able to buy a new-build home this large at this price! Home is priced to sell, with the lowest price per square foot than any other home in the area. Don't want to buy your next home at 6.5% interest? Buy this home with assumable FHA loan at 3.75% or sellers will consider seller's concessions to buy down interest rate! Motivated sellers
